author: coheigea
msg: - This commit saves information in WSDataRef about the encryption or signature algorithm used on the protected element.
- It also saves the signature and c14n algorithms in the WSSecurityEngineResult
- These can be used for validating what algorithms were used for signature or encryption
- I didn't commit the part of the patch relating to SAML assertions as its purpose was unclear, and no tests were supplied.
